data.description: Priced to Sell!   Beautifully brick 1.5 story home.  A cozy living room, hardwood floors, shaker style kitchen cabinets, appliances and granite countertops.   Hall leads to two bedrooms, full bath and half bath connect to bedroom, making this room a perfect option for a home office.  Upstairs you will find an oversized primary suite and beautiful full-bath! Enjoy backyard living with large back porch and a well maintained yard with barn.  Home Warranty Seller Paid. Inspection has been completed and repairs are needed. Will share inspection report.
